reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Brushes
reviews.reviewText: I was very happy with these brushes! The colors are so pretty, and the texture/tactile nature is very nice. The bristles are nice and soft, the handles easy enough to grip and use. I was also very happy that I DIDN’T notice any weird smells from production OR packaging.I’m REALLY happy especially with the eye brushes, as they all disperse the makeup very evenly, and they hold the shadow very well when transferring from case to face. They also blend very nicely, nothing comes out unevenly due to awkward or uneven bristles.All in all, very happy with this purchase. Good makeup brushes. 5 stars!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great selection of brushes for complete make-up application
reviews.reviewText: I was sceptical due to how low the price was when ordering these brushes, however I went ahead and ordered them anyway. I am not a professional , however, am not a beginner either , so each and every brush that I was looking for and needing was included in this large selection of brushes. The selection of brushes was amazing and the quality was actually better than I expected. From foundation brushes, to every eye shadow brush needed as well as lip/eyebrow etc. They are soft but the right firmness and they do apply well beyond my expectations. They came with a detailed card which gives a description for each and every brushes use for easy referencing as well as a durable plastic type bag to store them in if desired. I would recommend to anyone looking for decent affordable brushes. Well worth the price!
